input_full.body:
Agent-driven skill that:
- Reads the full test catalog (`TEST_CATALOG.md`)
- Builds and serves SBS-Test, keeping dev server live
- Performs manual screenshot review of the blueprint, checking everything captured in the test catalog
- Controls the browser via Chrome MCP extension -- clicking links, toggling proofs, switching themes, verifying interactions in real time
- Takes live screenshots throughout for evidence
- May spawn subagents for parallel review (e.g., visual vs functional)
- Reports findings in dialogue with user
- Logs discovered issues autonomously via `sbs_issue_log`

---
Created with [Claude Code](https://claude.ai/code)
